M|Core|it|Mobile-first always — ds for 375px then scale up
M|Core|it|Every cp must work at 320px minimum
M|Core|- Co|1 for all text (WCAG AA)
M|Core|it|Interactive elements min 44×44px touch target
M|Visu|it|One primary action per screen — no competing CTAs
M|Visu|it|Use whitespace as a ds element, not a gap-filler
M|Visu|it|Limit to 2 font sizes per cp
M|Visu|it|Use color to support meaning, never as the only signal
M|Layo|it|8px grid sy — all spacing multiples of 8
M|Layo|- Ma|1280px; comfortable reading width: 680px
M|Layo|it|Never center-align body text longer than 3 lines
M|Stat|- Ev|default, hover, active, focus, disabled states
M|Stat|it|Loading states required for any async operation > 300ms
M|Stat|it|Empty states must be designed — never show a blank page
M|Acce|it|All images require meaningful alt text
M|Acce|- Fo|none` w/o a replacement
M|Acce|it|Keyboard navigation must work for all interactive elements